text: Hutaytet al-Turkman (also spelled Hteitet Elturkman; ) is a Syrian village located in Markaz Rif Dimashq, Douma District. Hutaytet al-Turkman had a population of 4,800 in the 2004 census. ==References== Category:Populated places in Douma District Category:Villages in Syria
title: Hutaytet al-Turkman
